{"tid":1679782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好想好想贏  輸咗嘅話大家咩都冇","createTime":"2019-10-28T11:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T12:07:16.000Z","uid":313187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b631122f4b8462fbf301d6a55ca8cf0bbe23bf26","tid":1679782,"uid":313187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"我身邊有好多人冷卻左落嚟 <br />\n記唔記得我哋有幾多手足為咗自由殉道<br />\n唔好淨係靠香港人權民主法案<br />\n我哋仲可以靠自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W7AZdzXXJQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW7AZdzXXJQc&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=e569a0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W7AZdzXXJQc</a>"},{"pid":"455cf0b1da8fd23954667c70f773b0ee770c10fe","tid":1679782,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"f8bc7e051ea2c5f76c8591337fe9589cf345a4f3","tid":1679782,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"國際戰線，兩面夾擊！<br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n一、遊說戰線：<br />\n中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。<br />\n組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！<br />\n香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=1c3fd31c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=88d72f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n二、輿論戰線：<br />\n香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；<br />\n香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：<br />\n【我們香港人】倡導計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=7689e010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"b9e075daa0a012e44f9bdf717ed8d2b77eada3a4","tid":1679782,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aaf439e22ec68109ea79f35c5d5777393b14a57","tid":1679782,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"唔係冷卻<br />\n<br />\n係麻木<br />\n<br />\n我自己都開始有麻木嘅感覺<br />\n因為成件事拖得太耐又冇乜突破位"},{"pid":"478e078bdaf7d3a792a1e04c8879105445918e37","tid":1679782,"uid":313187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aaf439e22ec68109ea79f35c5d5777393b14a57","tid":1679782,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"唔係冷卻<br />\n<br />\n係麻木<br />\n<br />\n我自己都開始有麻木嘅感覺<br />\n因為成件事拖得太耐又冇乜突破位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"係吖 但係千其唔可以吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e21489196